https://www.journaldev.com/20292/android-mvvm-design-pattern

Configure -> build.gradle with implementation ROOM MVVM

Create classes in this sequence:

1 - Task (model entity)
2 - TaskDao (interface)
3 - DbRoomDatabase (connect database)
4 - TaskRepository (CRUD background)
5 - TaskViewModel (ViewModel - How to CRUD)
6 - TaskAdapter (To connect data values for show app, with:
                    a. RecyclerView
                    b. Widgets in activity)
6.1 - DatePickerFragment (To select day)
7 - TaskAddEditActivity (Add / Edit)
8 - TaskActivity (Show RecyclerView) --ATTENTION: import SearchView--

Configure -> AndroidManifest.xml
